 temperature and then store in an airtight container in the fridge for up to 5 days.\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_7639" align="alignnone" width="1024"]<a href="http://nu.spoonuniversity.com/apple-chickpea-hash/olympus-digital-camera-67/" rel="attachment wp-att-7639"><img class="size-large wp-image-7639" alt="Photo by Kendra Valkema" src="http://nu.spoonuniversity.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2013/01/P1019724-1024x768.jpg" width="1024" height="768" /></a> Photo by Kendra Valkema[/caption]	Meatless Mondays: Apple Chickpea Hash	http://spoonuniversity.com/recipe/apple-chickpea-hash/	\N	2014-01-14 18:55:29.094886	2014-01-14 18:55:29.094886	</strong>:\r\n1 large onion, sliced\r\n2 small apples or one large apple, diced\r\n1 can chickpeas\r\n1 tablespoon maple syrup\r\n1 handful kale\r\n\r\n<strong>
