um onion (roughly diced)\r\n1 bunch kale\r\n1 dollop Greek yogurt\r\nSpray of olive oil\r\n cup white cannellini beans\r\nGarlic powder\r\nSalt and pepper to taste\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_" align="aligncenter" width="1024"]<a href="http://upenn.spoonuniversity.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2013/11/10698992535_bac8b692a0_b.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-1300" alt="Photo by Connie Fan" src="http://upenn.spoonuniversity.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2013/11/10698992535_bac8b692a0_b.jpg" width="1024" height="683" /></a> Photo by Connie Fan[/caption]\r\n\r\n<strong>
